alerts.description:
There is a risk of wind gusts (level 1 of 4).
Max. gusts: ~ 55 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 70 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).
Height range: > 600 m; Max. gusts: 60-70 km/h; Wind direction: south-west then west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations < 80 km/h
